Package: castr
Type: Package
Title: Process CTD casts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jean-Olivier", "Irisson", email="irisson@normalesup.org",
    role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains functions to process data collected
    during CTD casts: smooth, despike, or integrate a variable; compute the
    depth of clines, of the deep chlorophyll maximum, of the bottom of the
    mixed layer (MLD); compute a stratification index. It also provides
    utilities to apply a function over a moving window along the cast, hence
    enabling the computation of moving averages, medians, etc.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
  R (>= 2.10),
  stats
